  "2026-07-14T02:30:00.404Z",codex-root,"Live verification correction: Sentry event 357f3deb67c0433090ce6dde4a980561 is handled=yes, CommandError exitCode=1, release pm-cli@2026.7.13, stack through package Object.run and the bundled CLI. It arrived during local release:gates, so the prior resolved/no-high claim is stale. Investigating the gate path before editing."
